# ── Xcode / CocoaPods (any depth) ─────────────────────
# The native ios/ project, Podfile and Podfile.lock ARE committed so
# Xcode Cloud can build. Pods/ is regenerated in CI (ci_post_clone.sh),
# so it stays ignored. Never commit user/build state or DerivedData.
**/Pods/
**/DerivedData/
**/xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
.xcode.env.local
# Codegen / build output produced by prebuild & pod install
apps/mobile/ios/build/

# ── Android (any depth) ───────────────────────────────
**/.gradle/
**/.cxx/
local.properties
*.hprof

# ── CI / Fastlane (keep ci_scripts/ committed!) ───────
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output/

# ── Misc ──────────────────────────────────────────────
*.orig
